<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Nurse Platform</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .welcome-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2c5aa0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üè• Nurse Platform</div>
            <h1>Welcome to Nurse Platform!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="welcome-text">Dear {{name}},</p>
            
            <p>Welcome to Nurse Platform! We're excited to have you join our community of healthcare professionals.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <h3>üéâ Your registration is complete!</h3>
                <p>Your account has been successfully created and is now pending verification by our admin team. This process typically takes 24-48 hours.</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>What happens next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account Review:</strong> Our admin team will review your credentials and documents</li>
                <li><strong>Verification:</strong> Once approved, your account will be marked as verified</li>
                <li><strong>Start Working:</strong> You'll be able to accept patient requests and start earning</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>While you wait, you can:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Complete your profile with additional information</li>
                <li>Upload your certifications and documents</li>
                <li>Set your availability and hourly rates</li>
                <li>Browse available patient requests</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing Nurse Platform!</p>
            <p><small>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you didn't register for this account, please ignore this email.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 